{"tid":833882,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（TVB或成最大贏家）【星美系爆煲】主席、執董全跳船 TVB揸6.5億CB危危乎","createTime":"2018-09-23T23:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T12:19:37.000Z","uid":54870,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf295b62b201aa79bdaf5be84053e2fa4fdbced","tid":833882,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T23:32:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180917/58691227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58691227&d=wPtz1vOvgA63T78xIRbl4E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5c50a543\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58691227&h=ee4be30e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180917/58691227</a><br />\n<br />\n星美系老闆覃輝疑「爆煲」！星美控股（198）上周五（9月14日）公佈，公司四名高層跳船，與此同時，TVB母公司電視廣播（511）持有星美控股一批可換股債券（CB），恐受事件波及。星美控股（198）仍然停牌<br />\n<br />\n據公告，集團收到多名人士之通知函，要求償還尚欠貸款及因而產生之利息。有本地財經傳媒《港股策略王》報道指，覃輝為北京頂級夜總會「天上人間」前老闆，而<span style=\"color: red;\">電視廣播亦曾認購一批CB，認購金額8300萬美元</span>（約6.52億港元），年利率為7.5%，為期兩年，可由訂約方互相協定延長至三年。至今電視廣播亦未作出新公告。"},{"pid":"be593b0af886ef2f3be4c48433745fd221f5f3dd","tid":833882,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T23:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/073314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F073314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6f192d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/073316_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F073316_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=64470a03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid"